le=\"color: blue;\">　　而</span><span style=\"color: green;\">司徒華</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">回憶錄</span><span style=\"color: red;\">指出</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港政府</span><span style=\"color: green;\">當天</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">用了</span><span style=\"color: green;\">直升機</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">點算</span>遊行<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數，數字</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">為</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">６７５０００人。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">　　２０１９０６０９</span>大遊行<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數</span><span style=\"color: red;\">肯定勁過</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２００３七一</span>大遊行<span style=\"color: green;\">（港鐵</span>都癱瘓），無<span style=\"color: red;\">雙倍</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">都有</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">倍半人數，</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">應該</span><span style=\"color: red;\">起碼用</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１.５倍</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">乘，</span><span style=\"color: red;\">起碼</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">是</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">下列</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">人數：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　主辦單位</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">應該</span><span style=\"color: red;\">公布</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">５０００００人</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">乘</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１.５倍</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">等於</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">７５００００人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">　　警方</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">應該</span><span style=\"color: red;\">統計</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">３５００００人</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">乘</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１.５倍</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">等於</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">５２５０００人<br />\n </span>　　唔知<span style=\"color: violet;\">邊個</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">回憶錄</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">應該</span><span style=\"color: red;\">指出</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">６７５０００人</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">乘</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１.５倍</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">等於</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">１０１２５００人</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">　　人在做，天在看，</span>做咁多衰嘢，遲早有報應，<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">　　真係</span><span style=\"color: red;\">好想</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">知道</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０１９</span><span style=\"color: purple;\">區議會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">選舉</span><span style=\"color: orange;\">與及</span><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">２０２０</span><span style=\"color: green;\">立法會</span><span style=\"color: red;\">選舉，睇吓</span><span style=\"color: green;\">香港市民</span><span style=\"color: violet;\">點揀？</span></strong></span>"}]}